attributeSource.infoString2: Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville

data.description: Great curb appeal to this hard to find one story 4 bedroom, 2 full bathrooms located in popular subdivision in Jacksonville, NC - Carolina Forest. Welcome guests with a quaint covered entryway. Convenient coat closet located near front door. Enter into a large living room with gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings with a breezy ceiling fan. Kitchen offers lots of cabinets and counter space, oven/range, built-in microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator. Nice size combination kitchen and dining area make it perfect for gatherings. Kitchen features a pantry for storage, dishwasher, range and refrigerator. Laundry room is conveniently located off the kitchen and near entrance into house from garage. Sleeping quarters are arranged on the right side of the house. Primary bedroom features private bathroom for owners with four piece ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, soaking tub with privacy window, separate shower and entrance into your walk in closet. 3 bedrooms share a central full bathroom with tub. Park your cars, bikes and toys in a 2 car attached garage a great feature on rainy days or for extra storage. Step out onto the back patio to enjoy barbecues and backyard games. Back yard features privacy fence and shed for storage. Home is conveniently located near schools, shopping, movie theatre, medical  and bases. Location, location, location makes this house your perfect next home.
